    label "section_1413_subsection_d_item_1"
    class_name "item"
    text "(1) Whenever the Administrator receives any application for issuance or transfer of a license for exploration or permit for commercial recovery, the Administrator shall transmit promptly a complete copy of such application to the Attorney General of the United States and the Federal Trade Commission."
  ]
